name: Mission Walk
description:
Beneath this floral pergola, the midday sun casts shadows, which draw your eyes down the path and invite your feet to follow. Inside the grounds of Mission San Juan Capistrano, this is just one of many lovely spots to visit.

#7 in the "Inviting You Through" series, a collection of windows, archways, and covered passages, which will invite you to look or travel through them, to see what's on the other side, or simply enjoy the journey of getting there.
